Next Conan's Hint:

433
00:24:04,220 --> 00:24:06,052
"Fish names".

434
00:24:06,052 --> 00:24:07,894
Eels, eels over rice, eel cookies,

435
00:24:07,894 --> 00:24:09,427
grilled eels, eel porridge, and eel soup.

436
00:24:09,676 --> 00:24:11,060
They're all different types of eel dishes.

